##A can of milk powder in an epidemic area

Wechat, southern weekly

Functional Introduction, here, read China! infzm.com

On February 22, the 14th day of the road closure in Fengcun, Huanggang, Hubei Province. In front of the camera, a mother placates her baby while recording a Vlog. The child writhed in its mother's arms from time to time as if searching for something.

"today our children have run out of milk powder, " the Vlog blogger from Huanggang, Hubei province, said on his video blog. Road closure of the village state, the opportunity to go out to purchase less and less, with the consumption of living materials, some daily necessities become scarce up. As a mother, to buy enough milk powder for their children has become an urgent problem.

Fortunately for the mother, with the help of the village Party secretary and the mother-and-child store, she got the much-needed milk powder that day and solved the immediate problem. But a similar situation is not unique in Huanggang.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
The streets of Wuhan in the rain and snow

On February 15, Snow was falling in the sky in Wuhan. In order to prevent and control the epidemic, most shops and stores still have not resumed business. Some netizens also began to report to the media through the Internet, at present, Wuhan began to appear infant formula out of stock situation. Some residents even worry, "milk powder will not be like a mask, become a powder hard to get. "

1
Shortage

1

Shortage

"recently, some citizens have reported that it is difficult to buy infant formula, and some supermarkets have also run out of infant formula. " On February 22, a media reporter raised the question at the 30th press conference of the COVID-19.

"infant formula is a very special product, very niche but very important and irreplaceable. At present, there are 1,600 tons of infant milk powder in Hubei Province, which can satisfy the drinking time of infants and young children in the province for more than one month, qin Jun, director of the Hubei Provincial Department of Commerce, admitted that "some time ago, because of the need for epidemic prevention, all mother-and-baby shops were not open, thus leading to a structural shortage. "

"Huanggang is one of the hardest hit areas in this epidemic, and the amount of dealer reserves can meet a month's demand, " said Zhou Hanghai, general manager of Qichun county's chain of thumb mother-and-baby living centers, in the face of the new situation during the epidemic, "Due to the closure of villages and road closures, it is very difficult to deliver goods and other links, plus the logistics is not yet smooth, some dealers are running out of stock. "

The problems of city closure and logistics stagnation have made Liu Yubiao, general manager of hypo-chem Biotechnology Co. , Ltd. in neighboring Hunan Province, feel the same as the Youlan brand team he leads. As a dairy industry practitioners, he found that in order to prevent and control the epidemic needs, mother and child stores are closed, "many children in the epidemic period of rations supply is very worrying. "

More importantly, the epidemic area some special environment, caused the separation between the mother and the baby. Front line medical workers, patients diagnosed with the disease and hospitalized for observation, and mothers serving in the quarantine zone can only be separated from their children temporarily.

Especially with the news that a mother was diagnosed with the virus during childbirth and that her baby was also diagnosed at birth, Cheng Feng, general manager of Beb, said, "It's a disaster that happens to babies at birth, " he said, noting that when a mother is infected, breast milk can not be provided and darling can not be held in her arms. "In this situation, babies are not safe. "

As the child's mother, long-time attention to the mother and baby field micro-blogger Yuan Jing introduced, "hospitals tend to stock up on infant formula for humanitarian and practical needs, " he said. But the rapid development of the epidemic has left such stocks stretched thin in Hubei Province. Yuan Jing observed that "the objective conditions do not allow" , making the role of infant formula more obvious, demand is more prominent.

"The youngest confirmed baby was only 30 hours old, and many mothers were quarantined when the baby was still breastfeeding, " said Liu, who has been following news reports about the outbreak since it began in mid-january.

Soon, Industry Data and information from partners across the country were put together in the hands of the Youlan team, ten times more than the usual number of member telephone inquiries, and generally asking supply-related questions, which further corroborated his judgment, "The current shortage of supplies is still very serious, because the outbreak came very suddenly, there was no advance preparation, coupled with logistics control and other reasons, Darling's rations were greatly affected, especially in the affected areas. "

2
Let's go

2

Let's go

Youlan's team found that due to the large amount of medical resources being skewed towards the prevention and control of the epidemic and the need for the prevention and control of the epidemic, ordinary people in the epidemic areas could not go smoothly to hospitals and other medical and health institutions, medical Health Consultation and related popular science work in epidemic areas have been greatly affected. Especially in the area of infant and young child health, the public needs in this area is often more urgent.

Facing the complex and severe situation, Youlan brand combines the advantages of the enterprise itself and focuses on two aspects. On the one hand, we should resume the business operation after the festival to ensure the supply of materials. On the other hand, we should focus on the nutrition requirement and scientific protection of the baby during the epidemic period.

In fact, in early February, Youlan brand through micro-blog and other self-media, on-line launched a series of epidemic prevention and infant nutrition-related popular science activities. Invite the relevant universities, first-line paediatrics, nutrition experts, and on this basis to establish online free consultation platform. "We have been providing expert consultation services and expert online lectures for Free Online, which is an online initiative. "

On the other hand, in Liu Yubiao's view, the most material shortage of the epidemic area is two things, one is medical supplies, one is people's livelihood materials.

Since the outbreak of the epidemic, the governments of Hubei Province and Wuhan City have put forward a series of policies to solve the problem of material supply. In this guiding ideology, commerce, transportation and other relevant departments have to supply goods and materials enterprises to solve problems, to protect the needs of Hubei People's "lifeline. ".

"Security of Supply" has also become the prime target of Youlan. "since February 7, the company has fully received the local government's distribution pass. " So while completing online support, Yulan started looking offline.

"We have a nationwide system of nearly 20,000 stores, together with more than 10,000 terminal partners who have distribution capacity and are qualified by the local government to deliver goods to your door without contact. " Get the pass, under the guidance of local governments and transport authorities, Youlan's distributors and partners in different regions began to arrange the delivery of goods. These measures have helped to alleviate the shortage of food rations for newborns and young children.

Transport convoy for delivery

As the Netherlands imported organic baby formula blue, its origin in the Netherlands has not been affected by the epidemic, so production and other links are functioning normally, ample supplies. Together with the entire transport process through the china-eu express line, to ensure that from production to transport, not affected by the epidemic, to continue to supply domestic users.

"The special cars are sent to the terminal outlets in each city, that is, to distributors and partners. After they get the local distribution license for special infant rations, they adopt the online-to-offline, centralized-to-offline distribution and contactless distribution method, " Liu said, according to photos displayed by Liu, distribution personnel with consumers, through the line tied bucket, small basket, etc. , goods up the stairs, there are plastic bags containing materials to the door, and then back to a safe distance, waiting for consumers to take away goods, ensure the supply of goods.

As the campaign began, the Youlan team also began to realize that if they wanted to contribute more, they needed to find professional people to go with them.

While the Youlan team has been working around the clock on a Pro-bono Action Plan, the partners of the Guangdong Zhong Nanshan Medical Foundation, which continues to assist frontline hospitals, are also worried about shortages of supplies other than protective supplies. "In addition to protective materials, including physiological pads, milk powder, instant noodles and other materials, there is a need in hospitals. "

Guided by the idea of "professional people doing professional things, " Youlan's team found the Guangdong Zhongnanshan Medical Foundation, and after a series of exchanges and communication, uu Foundation, Zhong Nanshan Medical Foundation, charity associations around the world, Sina News, Sina Child Care and other organizations, bring their expertise into play, jointly opened the "Blue Organic, love and vitality, " the professional guardian of the new public welfare activities.

3
Served

3

Served

"More than twenty-two thousand cans, nearly ten million yuan worth of Youlan organic formula milk powder and one million, two hundred and forty thousand yuan worth of protective materials, " Liu said of the campaign, "baby rations, face masks and disinfectants, with a total value of 11 million yuan, " he said. The supplies began arriving in mid-february at first-line hospitals, allowing hospitals to transport them on a regular basis according to actual demand.

In response to the needs of the epidemic, Youlan from domestic and foreign procurement, mobilization of a number of protective materials, including many high-level protective supplies. In the face of their own team is still short of protective supplies, Youlan team but unanimously decided that this batch of high-level protective supplies, priority to the front-line medical staff.

The material reserve is gradually abundant, but under the epidemic prevention and control system in Hubei, the transportation is still a problem, the last kilometer material delivery, becomes the biggest challenge that Liu Yubiao's Youlan team faces.

Mobilize more forces to participate in "Yilan Organic, love and vitality, " another major goal of the public welfare projects. Youlan team will once again focus on the dealers and partners throughout Hubei Team, issued the initiative, hope that more partners with Youlan together, "retrogressive, chi-aid Hubei. ".

As the partner of Youlan, Li Xiaoli, general manager of Hubei Aixinmingyang Trading Co. , Ltd. and her team chose to join Youlan's "retrograde" army at the first time. "Working 14 to 16 hours a day, " just to get supplies to the front line as quickly as possible.

As a result of the epidemic, there was some panic hoarding of milk powder in some areas. In Li Xiaoli's view, milk powder was "a good time to sell" , while Youlan's choice was to donate rather than sell, this made her feel "this is a great love of a business. " Driven by great love, Li Xiaoli and her team delivered 900 tins of 75 Youlan baby formula to the First People's Hospital of Guangshui.

Li Xiaoli is not alone, in order to solve the most intractable last kilometer problem, more dealers and partners in the first time to join the YOULAN initiative.

Partner Foshan, Hubei Province baby beauty is reaching out

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Since the outbreak, all kinds of information have been influencing Cheng Feng. "Youlan just put forward this kind of initiative at this time. I am willing to cooperate with Youlan to do this. " Under YOULAN's initiative, beb, general manager of the baby friendly chain, and his team set out to prepare. Due to the impact of the epidemic, logistics enterprises a large number of material accumulation, in order to timely delivery of goods to the hands of the most needed people, we need to go to the warehouse to search, again and again to find and move, sweat wet the clothes of the staff.

On February 18,900 sets of 75 youlan baby formula milk powder were sent to Xiaogan City Hospital of traditional Chinese medicine and Xiaogan City First People's Hospital by Cheng Feng and his team.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Materials delivered to the First People's Hospital of Xiaogan city

As an old batch of partners, in the face of a lot of problems arising under the epidemic, Qichun county thumb mother and Baby Life Museum Chain General Manager Zhou Hanghai on the action of Youlan is very recognized. "They overcame many difficulties and were able to deliver the products to the designated locations of various distributors and also to the designated donated hospitals, which they were able to do with great efforts. " A total of 33 youlan infant formulas were delivered to Qichun county maternal and child health care hospital.

Parents who receive donated formula

Cans of milk powder in exchange for thank you again and again, "when the shortage of milk powder delivered to the hands of the new baby's parents, their eyes of sorrow into joy, " Zhou Hanghai felt that their efforts and countless partners have not been in vain, it's all worth it.

On a normal day, a can of milk powder may be a necessity of life, but it has nothing to do with life. Under the epidemic situation, a can of milk powder has become the epidemic area people eagerly waiting for tight supplies, carrying a great love. When a can of milk powder to overcome traffic control, manpower shortage and other problems, sent to the epidemic area, in exchange for not only from the epidemic area medical team and parents of infants and children's thanks, but also for the recognition of the youlan brand.
